<link path="ixml/help.xml">The Circle Help</link> :: <link path="ixml/commands.xml">Commands</link> :: <link path="ixml/cmd_listen.xml">listen</link>

Syntax: /listen [+ or -] channel[,channel...]
         
Modify the list of channels you are listening to.
       
Example:
       
      /listen #welcome
      /listen - #trek
      /listen + #buffy

To list the channels you are currently listening to, type

      /listen

